                <h1>How to Create a Transparent Background in Photoshop</h1>
                <p>Creating a transparent background in Photoshop is essential for graphic design and photo editing. Use the Magic Wand or Quick Selection tool to isolate your subject, then simply remove the background. Save in PNG format to maintain transparency. This technique allows for seamless layering and enhances your design's versatility.</p>
